Name: MILF HUNTER
About the game: Milf Hunter - is a casual game with a simple puzzle. A game that can change your idea of ​​the planets and help you discover them from an unexpected side. 8 representatives of different planets are waiting for you, each of which will surprise you with its originality and uniqueness! Here you will feel like a real space explorer and pioneer! Features: 8 beautiful alien girls who are in a hurry to reveal the secrets of the Universe for you 32 levels that will truly take you into space Each successfully completed level will give you a surprise Intensive training of your logical thinking The ability to chat with unearthly girls in the truest sense of the word Enjoyment from every space representative of this game About the characters: Girl Mercury is the smallest and hottest alien personality. Possesses cunning and high intelligence, he values ​​the same in the interlocutor. Girl Venus is a real goddess of love and pleasure, but in the eternal search for her companion. Girl Earth, she has, as they say, 'everything is with you', therefore she is demanding in relationships. Girl Mars - seemingly unapproachable and cold, but as soon as you get to know her better, she reveals herself in a completely different amlua. Girl Jupiter is the owner of the most powerful magnetic field, so it will be difficult for you to tear yourself away from her. Girl Saturn - an unusual appearance attracts all lovers of astronomy and 53 faithful companions always turn around her. Will you be able to win your place too? Girl Uranus is a cold and windy representative who dreams that her heart will finally be warmed and all internal hurricanes will be calmed down. Girl Neptune is the most distant and unapproachable, but soft inside. She is ready to open up if you gain her trust.
